Text: Damn her...!
Zeta?!
A message from your goddess... Nonsense, all of it!

A message of the Goddess is nothing but a message of
the Goddess.
You... You've been following me!
Zetaâ€•
I have not been following you.

I am only learning now that you are a part of the
Shadow Garden.
Stop messing with me!
I will handle her! You deal with the Templars!
No, I will handle her! She's already seen my face!
Huh?!

The leader of the Templars is the Church's sacred
prophet. This is too good to be true.

You expect me to keep quiet about your charade? By my
own hands...I...will...kill you!

I am not able to kill you. And you are not able to
kill me.

Why, you may ask? Because this reunion is the will of
the Goddess Beatrix.

We, who have been brought together under fate by the
Goddess, cannot kill each other.
Keep telling yourself that!

Zeta, your strikes are off! Fall back! Regain your
composure!
Die, apostate!
Death to the heretics!

Spreading out the Garden to maintain secrecy appears
to have backfired...
Even so, my sword arm will never lose its strength!

Zeta! The prophet is yours! I will take care of the
Templars!
She... She is really good...!

I knew from last time that you can't even be compared
to the other Templars!
You also seemed to retract your claws that time.
She just dodged that...without looking!

You are clearly...an enemy that must be wiped out no
matter what!
Why do you divide people into "enemies" and "allies"?

Let me explain something to you, O Holy Sister with
your crazy prophecies... That's because you guys kill
the possessed.

Scum like you that crush innocent girls like they are
insects... You're the enemy!!
Even though the existence of the possessed is a sin?

You would understand if you've ever been possessed!
Try teaching me to be thankful for the one-sided
selfishness of your church's dogma!

You're saying that you were once possessed?! That you
were cured?

That... That is such a boon! The Goddess saved my
friend!
Don't just decide that we're friends!

And, if there are boons in this world, then they can
only be the ones given by my lord.
Your lord? Who is he?!
The survivors are on the run! I'm going after them!
Ack...! Out of my way!
Ngh...! This is nothing!
You... You're risking your life?!

If I can save even a few of their lives, then saving
them is the duty of the one blessed with conveying
the will of the Goddess Beatrix.
Shut up!!!
Oh no!

I see she took advantage of your power to put
distance between you.

I look forward...to meeting you again, my friend.
You who has been blessed by the Goddess...
Ack...!
What the hell!
What's going on here?!
Zetaâ€•
Agh...!

Useless! The kitty cat just let them get away!
Why didn't she kill her prey?!

You really are useless! I'm gonna kill you,
you coward!
Delta! Calm downâ€•
Ack... Her raw strength is unbelievable!
Delta!
Grr...
Gaaaahhh!!!
Damn it...!
Lady Alphaâ€”

Templars are an assassination organization led by
a prophet of the Church. We can now clearly see the
enemy that must be cast down by the Gardenâ€•

That a prophet is leading a murderous group hidden in
church dogma... This is looking more like war.

We will have to be more careful about what Mitsugoshi
does in future.
Our plans...will need...rewriting....

Should return home, think... We have that secret
base...for that...
Eta... You're right. That's what we shall do.

We achieved the main objectives of this operation.
We exposed the leader of the Templars and stamped
out a threat to the Garden.

With this, let's return...to the ancient city
of Alexandria.
That's right... Our fight has only just begun...

Here, we Templars, officially recognize the Shadow
Garden, an organization that we have been monitoring,
as a target of the inquisition.

In the name of the Goddess Beatrix, we must cleanse
them in secrecy. Wipe them all out!
Haaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa!!!

Zeta...you have been blessed by the Goddess. I must
save you from the heretics as well.

Yes, you...are my first friend. A friend sent to me
by the Goddess...
